      "title": "Linked Discourses 22 ",
      "expandable": false
    },
    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:1.1",
          "pli": "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. ",
          "en": "At Sāvatthī. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:1.2",
          "pli": "Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā … pe … bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: ",
          "en": "Then Venerable Ānanda went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:1.3",
          "pli": "“sādhu me, bhante, bhagavā saṅkhittena dhammaṃ desetu, yamahaṃ bhagavato dhammaṃ sutvā eko vūpakaṭṭho appamatto ātāpī pahitatto vihareyyan”ti. ",
          "en": "“Sir, may the Buddha please teach me Dhamma in brief. When I’ve heard it, I’ll live alone, withdrawn, diligent, keen, and resolute.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:2.1",
          "pli": "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, ānanda, ",
          "en": "“What do you think, Ānanda? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:2.2",
          "pli": "rūpaṃ niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti? ",
          "en": "Is form permanent or impermanent?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:2.3",
          "pli": "“Aniccaṃ, bhante”. ",
          "en": "“Impermanent, sir.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:2.4",
          "pli": "“Yaṃ panāniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vā taṃ sukhaṃ vā”ti? ",
          "en": "“But if it’s impermanent, is it suffering or happiness?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:2.5",
          "pli": "“Dukkhaṃ, bhante”. ",
          "en": "“Suffering, sir.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:2.6",
          "pli": "“Yaṃ panāniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vipariṇāmadhammaṃ, kallaṃ nu taṃ samanupassituṃ: ",
          "en": "“But if it’s impermanent, suffering, and liable to fall apart, is it fit to be regarded thus: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:2.7",
          "pli": "‘etaṃ mama, esohamasmi, eso me attā’”ti? ",
          "en": "‘This is mine, I am this, this is my self’?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:2.8",
          "pli": "“No hetaṃ, bhante”. ",
          "en": "“No, sir.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:2.9",
          "pli": "“Vedanā … ",
          "en": "“Is feeling … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:2.10",
          "pli": "saññā … ",
          "en": "perception … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:2.11",
          "pli": "saṅkhārā … ",
          "en": "choices … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:2.12",
          "pli": "viññāṇaṃ niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti? ",
          "en": "consciousness permanent or impermanent?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:2.13",
          "pli": "“Aniccaṃ, bhante”. ",
          "en": "“Impermanent, sir.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:2.14",
          "pli": "“Yaṃ panāniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vā taṃ sukhaṃ vā”ti? ",
          "en": "“But if it’s impermanent, is it suffering or happiness?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:2.15",
          "pli": "“Dukkhaṃ, bhante”. ",
          "en": "“Suffering, sir.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:2.16",
          "pli": "“Yaṃ panāniccaṃ dukkhaṃ vipariṇāmadhammaṃ, kallaṃ nu taṃ samanupassituṃ: ",
          "en": "“But if it’s impermanent, suffering, and liable to fall apart, is it fit to be regarded thus: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:2.17",
          "pli": "‘etaṃ mama, esohamasmi, eso me attā’”ti? ",
          "en": "‘This is mine, I am this, this is my self’?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:2.18",
          "pli": "“No hetaṃ, bhante”. ",
          "en": "“No, sir.” … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:2.19",
          "pli": "“Evaṃ passaṃ … pe … ",
          "en": "“Seeing this … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:2.20",
          "pli": "nāparaṃ itthattāyāti pajānātī”ti. ",
          "en": "They understand: ‘… there is no return to any state of existence.’” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:2.21",
          "pli": "Dasamaṃ. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:2.22",
          "pli": "Diṭṭhivaggo pañcamo. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:3.1",
          "pli": "Ajjhattikaṃ etaṃmama, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:3.2",
          "pli": "Soattā nocamesiyā; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:3.3",
          "pli": "Micchāsakkāyattānu dve, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:3.4",
          "pli": "Abhinivesā ānandenāti. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:3.5",
          "pli": "Uparipaṇṇāsako samatto. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:4.1",
          "pli": "Anto dhammakathikā vijjā, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:4.2",
          "pli": "kukkuḷaṃ diṭṭhipañcamaṃ; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:4.3",
          "pli": "Tatiyo paṇṇāsako vutto, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:4.4",
          "pli": "nipātoti pavuccatīti. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.159:4.5",
          "pli": "Khandhasaṃyuttaṃ samattaṃ. ",
          "en": "The Linked Discourses on the aggregates are complete."
        }
      ],
